# ❌ Error: Invoice Mismatch

## 🧩 Problem
Invoice does not match PO details.

## 🌍 Scenario
Invoice blocked due to quantity/price mismatch.

## 🔍 Root Cause
- Incorrect PO data  
- Pricing mismatch  
- Quantity difference  

## ⚠️ Common Errors
- Quantity exceeded  
- Price mismatch  

## ✅ Solution
1. Compare PO & invoice  
2. Correct mismatch  
3. Re-submit  

## 🧠 Approach
Check source document (PO) first.

## 🎯 Learning
Invoice always depends on PO accuracy.
